name: kipkay_iphone_vs_lasers
description: This is a YouTube video from a creator named Kit K and it's the iPhone 5 versus lasers and a flashlight. And in the video he destroys the iPhone by burning it with the lasers and then putting the flashlight on top of it. I loved this video when I was in elementary school and I tried to replicate it myself using normal flashlights and I played the same song that it used in the background when I made those videos as well. He just destroys the phone using the flashlight and lasers.

name: rust_note_installer
description: This is the output from when I used homebrew installer to install the Rust programming language and the compiler and everything and this is the output that it gave that included information on where it installed it on my computer and so on.

name: C0191
description: This is a video of me riding my unicycle over to the Walmart neighborhood market. I'm going from my home to the grocery store on my unicycle and I record the adventure on my unicycle as I go down the street and arrive at the grocery store.

name: C0200
description: This is a video of us in the Vienna airport arriving for the first time and collecting our baggage.

name: C0201
description: This is a video of the spot I had in my relative Parastou's house in Vienna when I went to visit. It shows the bed that I was sleeping on during my visit.
An audio recording of the Austrian Airlines flight from Munich to Vienna. The mini-airplane had some cool sound effects and was very loud.

name: C0203
description: A video of a local park that I visited in Vienna, it was near my Aunt Peristou's house and I showed the park and the surrounding area in the video.

name: C0204
description: A video of my family members and I in the metro station in Vienna. I show us getting tickets in the station.

name: C0205
description: A video of a family gathering that we had at my own Paris student's house in Vienna. It was my first time meeting a lot of the family members and we were all over for dinner. I show most of the people who were there in the video.

name: C0207
description: A video of me showing the train in Austria. This was the train coming from Graz to Vienna. And I show the interior of it with the seats and my computer setup.

name: C0208
description: A video of me in Vienna with my mom and her cousin Waffa. We were walking in the night time to get to an Italian pizza restaurant that was about a mile's walk away.

name: C0209
description: A video showing the Italian restaurant that we were at with my family in Vienna. It shows my family members and the surrounding area of where we were sitting.

name: C0210
description: A video showing a neighborhood street in Vienna, which shows the cars passing by on the street as well as the buses.

name: C0211
description: This is a video of a neighborhood street in Vienna. It shows buses and cars passing by as well as the nearby Karl Marx Hof Park and stations.

name: C0214
description: This is a demonstration of a creative bathroom door mechanism that we found in a coffee shop in Austria. It was the city of Thule. And it shows a coffee maker style item hanging from a rope that opens and closes the bathroom door. And my mom shows it working.

name: DSC01608
description: This is a photo of my grandfather, Baba Farazin, at the airport terminal. He had lost his phone and he's talking to the TSA worker about it.

name: R1-06851-004A
description: A picture showing the view from my relative Parastou's house in Vienna. This is the view from the porch and it shows a few apartment buildings and trees.

name: R1-06851-006A
description: A photo of my dad's friend Reza and his wife Maryam and I together at the Vienna Central Hospital where Reza worked. We had just finished eating food at the cafeteria and asked someone to take this picture of us in the cafeteria.

name: R1-06851-008A
description: This is a photo I took of a street in Austria with my Kodak Funsaver. It was a very beautiful photo of the street. There are a few cars on the road lined up with some apartment buildings in the background. And there's two ladies wearing black clothing in the right side of the image that are on the metro tracks. And that's it.

name: R1-06851-010A
description: This is a photo of my aunt Leila and her husband Hassan sitting on a couch in their house watching TV. I took this photo right before I left their house during my visit to Graz, Austria.

name: R1-06851-011A
description: This is a photo of my aunt Leila and I standing together. This was taken at the preschool that she works at in Austria when I went to visit her for the first time there. It's taken right behind where the kids were eating their lunch.

name: R1-06851-014A
description: This is a photo of my family sitting on a bench in Austria during our trip. It shows them sitting on a bench in the middle of the city center. There's a lot of people in the background.

name: R1-06851-017A
description: This is a picture of the 680 highway that I took on my Kodak Funsaver camera. It shows the highway as we were driving and it's nearby the place I worked at REI and near the 680 junction with 580. It shows the road and I've taken it by putting the camera outside of the window and taking the photo quickly while my mom was driving.

name: graz_train_ticket
description: This is a train ticket for my trip to Graz to visit my Aunt Leyla. It was a ticket I used to get from the Vienna Central Station to the Graz Central Station.

name: parsa_passport_usa
description: This is a scan of my United States passport. It shows the front page with my signature and also my picture and information.

name: shiva_passport_usa
description: This is a picture of the United States passport of my mom, Shiva.
